dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.securecommunication

Interface ITlsCryptoCipherSuite

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface ITlsCryptoCipherSuite
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    ITlsCryptoCipherSuite: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents a cipher suite for describing cryptographic operations in the context of establishing a connection of ApplicationEndpoints that is protected by TLS.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
